The paper deals with a machine learning model that is able to continually learn and generalize concepts to new domains without forgetting the past learned knowledge. This falls under the domain of continual learning, which is a subfield of machine learning. The paper also mentions the use of generative models and embedding spaces, which are commonly used in the subfields of deep learning and natural language processing. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CL (Computation and Language), cs.CV (Computer Vision), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
